'''Pukete Bridge''' is a concrete [[box girder bridge]] in [[Hamilton, New Zealand|Hamilton]], [[New Zealand]], spanning the [[Waikato River]].

In February 2011 an upgrade will begin to expand to number of lanes to four. It is expected to be completed by late 2013.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/waikato-times/news/3953622/Ring-road-expansion-planned |title=Ring road expansion planned |first-Nikki |last=Preston |newspaper=[[Waikato Times]] |publisher=[[Fairfax New Zealand]] |date=24 July 2010 |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5sx2vHdPl |archivedate=23 September 2010 |accessdate=23 September 2010}}</ref>

